WEBVTT

00:04.433 --> 00:06.433
It's time for the contest

00:06.458 --> 00:09.570
that's taking America by storm,
"stop that deejay.

00:09.851 --> 00:11.476
Fine. Bring it on, chump.

00:11.477 --> 00:13.477
So we got through the holidays
in one piece, right?

00:13.478 --> 00:15.478
but the big bearded guy
in the red suit

00:15.479 --> 00:17.212
deserves one last trivia
shout-out.

00:17.312 --> 00:19.977
Now, we know he didn't deliver
all these presents by himself.

00:20.077 --> 00:23.578
So, name for me all of
Santa's 9 reindeer.

00:23.580 --> 00:26.531
Oh, I know this.
Prancer, Dancer--

00:29.585 --> 00:31.303
"Forgive me, sweetheart.

00:31.305 --> 00:33.471
I tried to make it right."

